Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.62,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Leo Rugiens!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:56.86,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got,\NCaptain of the Crimson Lion Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,In the instant you attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:12.17,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,for just a moment, the barrier's \Nmana thins in places.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.38,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I aimed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:17.80,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.30,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Rades, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:24.77,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you possess extraordinary abilities \Nand polish them to their fullest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.27,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,without a righteous spirit,\Nyour deeds are nothing but violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:33.15,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No one will acknowledge something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:39.95,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get stronger so things like \Nthis don't give me so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.61,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for you to \Nbe cheering just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:47.08,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I think everything's just about ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.58,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some lively sow's mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.22,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:18.07,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:27.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:41.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:49.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:54.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:03:00.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.55,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.43,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:33.31,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I have magic that's stronger\Nthan anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:38.98,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I studied everything there was about my \Nmagic, polished my skills, and prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.32,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,All for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.87,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,For years... and years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:52.14,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.06,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can save the thanks! Just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.19,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.94,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Ignis Columna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:51.22,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?! I made him \Nevaporate with intense firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.25,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.94,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You are definitely a man worthy\Nof leading this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.44,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally saluted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.24,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:14.81,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I've got as much magic as a royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.71,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame-Binding Magic: Leo Palma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.42,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.98,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.22,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.73,top,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.73,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There are many questions I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.23,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I will be \Nconfiscating your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.44,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.95,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What is this grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.58,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.34,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one page?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.74,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.77,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,He can only use one spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.17,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.95,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.18,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna look down on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:28.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you think of any other way to get \Npeople to acknowledge your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:37.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You have amazing magic, and you were\Nstrong enough to claw your way up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I'll lend you my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:54.64,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What you lacked to overcome adversity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.89,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,was a righteous heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.65,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Pay for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.65,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.99,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:14.13,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible for you to beat \Na captain on your own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.91,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.74,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.71,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer volume of your magic isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.53,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also reaching my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.65,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're through acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.57,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, things are \Ngoing to go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.43,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,All for our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.93,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,West District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.70,main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.98,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.98,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I think I'll go have some dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.26,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.90,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,I will decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.43,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,541)}East District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.53,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.17,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our lodgings and \Nwash off all this sweat, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.21,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.00,main,Guy A,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Blue Rose Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.11,main,Lady 1,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte is so elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.29,main,Lady 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte is so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:10.92,main,Lady 3,0000,0000,0000,,Sol is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.68,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.90,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What is their motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.92,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,539)}Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.49,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're in the marked areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:52.92,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.81,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.61,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.48,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.45,main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.70,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.21,main,Lady 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte... disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.21,main,Lady 3,0000,0000,0000,,Sol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.83,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.15,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that we're at least
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.11,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,a few hundred kilometers \Naway from the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:02.70,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,They got us! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.82,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,They managed to infiltrate the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:11.63,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I figured they must've had a rather \Nskilled spatial magic user, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.05,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,To think they were able \Nto send us all this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.78,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.51,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights' mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.97,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:31.48,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This is unprecedented spatial magic. \NWas there another spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.25,main,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.24,main,Lady A,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:53.76,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,To think the great Magic Knights would \Nall fall for a silly trap like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.50,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:01.18,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to play with the stragglers, \Nbut it looks like I won't have to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:06.52,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I'd better use this \Ntime to get some nice, young mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:11.34,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Ash Curse Magic: Ash Absorbing Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.32,main,Man E,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.11,main,Lady C,0000,0000,0000,,No! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.38,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.60,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is silky smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.62,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Even water would bounce right off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.38,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,No! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:41.76,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting all cute, you sow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.10,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza! W-Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:58.40,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you a handsome young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:05.59,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think I'm pretty?\NHow old do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.62,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:10.29,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you? You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.26,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a monster?! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.84,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.76,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I guess someone was able to \Nescape that spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:40.61,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're hot {\i1}and{\i0} my type.\NSay, want to have some fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.83,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:07.68,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're hot {\i1}and{\i0} my type.\NSay, want to have some fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.10,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.10,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.49,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Ash Curse Magic: Cheerful Ash Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.36,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,These are curse bullets \Nwith various curses inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.29,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know what you'll \Nget until they hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:43.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people? What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.47,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. Look at you, \Nwith such ample time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:50.05,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you're hot, \NI guess I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:54.47,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to eliminate someone.\NThat's our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.10,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.85,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think it is, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.99,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm definitely not going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.27,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're working with at least one other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,A spatial magic user must have \Ninfiltrated the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.37,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.13,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Have they already fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.75,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you might've sent \Nthe rest of the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:30.39,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have enough power \Nto take over the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.89,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that this was \Njust to go after the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.39,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,King's Quarters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.97,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You've made it clear that \Nyour motive is revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,but what are you and the \Nothers after overall?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.91,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Our true motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.92,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is you, Fuegoleon Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.38,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.68,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.43,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.89,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This is spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.69,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Nothing ventured, nothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.39,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.69,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:06.42,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks keep coming. She has\Na tremendous amount of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:10.07,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These ash bullets themselves \Ndon't do much damage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.05,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.60,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? It looks like you're \Nhaving a hard time getting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.00,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you've been hit with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.45,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I... can barely see anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:32.01,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gradually losing sensation\Nthroughout my body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.97,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:42.02,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are also going... This is her power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:47.90,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My Ash Curse Magic: Cheerful Ash \NDestruction works very gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.46,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,First, your eyes stop \Nworking, then your ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.38,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,and then your body stops moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:59.91,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for having the \Ninsolence to call me an old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.49,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,People expected a lot\Nfrom my four-leaf clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:08.46,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I even joined the top Magic \NKnights squad, the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.88,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.50,flashback,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about a four-leaf clover?\NThat stupid peasant, getting a big head...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:23.25,flashback,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. He lacks the talent worthy to \Nbe a member of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.89,flashback,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.65,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,All those voices around me don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:34.40,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only bettering myself so I won't lose. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.57,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.72,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What defeated that guy was \Na power I just happened upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.12,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,one that I can't control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.58,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.75,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That power doesn't seem \Nto want to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:57.26,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I was able to \Navoid the spatial magic earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:02.10,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,was because something other\Nthan my own power reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:07.06,flashback,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're expecting \Nanything from that peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.30,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:12.11,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why I'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.95,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.53,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You have to aim properly, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:31.58,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,If you say, "I'm sorry, miss," and adorably \Nbeg for your life, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.13,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a... chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.03,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.18,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel... anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.70,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the flow of mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:10.06,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that mages with wind-based \Nmana are excellent at detecting mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.23,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With all five senses cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and his back against the wall,\NYuno's finely honed concentration
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,demonstrated an astonishing\Nability to detect mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:20.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and was attempting to go beyond even that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:27.61,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up and beg for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.99,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'm just \Ngoing to have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:36.02,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things I want \Nto ask you. Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.57,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.59,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.25,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.08,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:51.04,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:54.33,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,to Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.17,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:06.85,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire... \NThe legendary four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.36,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mana is gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.61,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,This sensation... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:29.04,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,He's controlling the mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:35.10,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The spirit has constantly \Nbeen sending me mana signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:40.13,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was relying so much on my sight and \Nhearing that I wasn't noticing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:45.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just tell you one thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,hate losing more than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Magic: Sylph's Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.15,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,No! I have to use the magic \NI stole to defend myself, or I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.41,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:46.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:56.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:02.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:07.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:10.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:18.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:21.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:23.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:32.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:38.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:41.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
