Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.75,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:00.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(521,1)}Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:59.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get the wind \Nspirit to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:07.62,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I shall name her Bell,\Nand today is Bell's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:10.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This cake is for you, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:11.66,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Should we say you're one year old?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.62,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:19.37,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:22.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Make a wish and blow out the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.17,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.69,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:37.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:41.94,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What did \Nyou do with my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.44,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Answer wisely, or you shall face my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:46.98,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon! You... Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.53,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 25: "Adversity."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 25\N\N{\fs18}Adversity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:51.82,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calm at all times...
